      "content": "hey so im a student in berlin and things are super stressful right now with finals coming up. im currently on sertraline for my depression but i feel like it's not quite doing enough to help with the anxiety/mood swings. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine to help boost my mood naturally since it's just a herbal supplement. do u think it's okay to take them both together?",
